utterances.speaker: JUAN WILLIAMS, HOST

utterances.speaker: YOVANOVITCH

utterances.speaker: YOVANOVITCH

utterances.speaker: NUNES

utterances.speaker: YOVANOVITCH
utterances.utterance: No, I have not.

utterances.utterance: Okay, there is that. Many of the members of Congress on the Republican side said too that they would not have tweeted that. utterances.speaker: SEWELL
utterances.utterance: How has it affected your family?

utterances.speaker: YOVANOVITCH
